Boots of Speed		TYPE:Wondrous Item.Boot.Attunement		WT:0	SOURCEPAGE:DMG	SLOTS:2	EQMOD:MAGIC_ITEM_RARE	SPROP:While you wear these boots, you can take a Bonus Action to click the boots' heels together. If you do, the boots double your Speed, and any creature that makes an Opportunity Attack against you has Disadvantage on the attack roll. Ify ou click your heels together again, you end the effect. When you've used the boots' property for a total of 10 minutes, the magic ceases to function for you until you finish a Long Rest.|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Attunement,Boots of Speed	DEFINE:Attunement_Boots_of_Speed|0	BONUS:VAR|Attunement_Boots_of_Speed|1	SPROP:Not attuned to Item|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Attunement,Boots of Speed
